snippet.title: Dwarf Delve - Trailer
snippet.description: Collect precious resources as a dwarven miner in Dwarf Delve. Explore randomized quarries and biomes, collecting priceless ore before time runs out and the mine collapses. Prevent failure by building key infrastructure or risk digging a little deeper to excavate hidden artifacts. Upgrade gear and tools with the riches earned, then dive into the mines once again, hopefully not for the last time…
